# Chart interaction — crosshair + tooltip

Every interactive time-series chart in this app **must** show:

1. **Vertical dashed crosshair** at the hovered x-position
2. **HTML tooltip** with the snapped date/period and value(s) at that x

Do not rely on native SVG `<title>` alone. Do not use per-point `onMouseEnter` without a plot-area crosshair.

## Canonical reference

`src/routes/company/[cik]/features/insider-transactions/.../insider-transactions-chart/insider-transactions-chart.tsx`

## Required behavior

- Wrap the SVG in `relative` container; tooltip is `absolute`, `pointer-events-none`, `z-10`
- Transparent `rect` over the plot area with `cursor-crosshair`, `onMouseMove`, `onMouseLeave`
- Snap hover to the nearest x-bucket / data point (not free-floating pixel coords)
- On hover:
  - Render vertical line: `stroke="#71717a"`, `strokeWidth="1.5"`, `strokeDasharray="5 4"`, from plot top to plot bottom
  - Emphasize active point(s) with larger circles + white stroke
  - Dim non-hovered series/points (`opacity={0.35}`) when applicable
- Tooltip content:
  - Date/period label (`text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500`)
  - One or more value rows with label + formatted value (`font-mono`)
  - Position with `left: (hover.x / CHART_WIDTH) * 100%`, `transform: translateX(-50%)`, `top: 8`

## SVG structure checklist

```tsx
<div className="relative overflow-x-auto">
  {hover ? (
    <div className="pointer-events-none absolute z-10 ..." style={{ left: `${(hover.x / CHART_WIDTH) * 100}%`, top: 8, transform: "translateX(-50%)" }}>
      {/* date + values */}
    </div>
  ) : null}
  <svg viewBox={`0 0 ${CHART_WIDTH} ${CHART_HEIGHT}`}>
    {/* grid, paths, points */}
    {hover ? (
      <>
        <line x1={hover.x} x2={hover.x} y1={PADDING.top} y2={CHART_HEIGHT - PADDING.bottom} stroke="#71717a" strokeWidth="1.5" strokeDasharray="5 4" />
        {/* emphasized active dots */}
      </>
    ) : null}
    <rect x={PADDING.left} y={PADDING.top} width={plotWidth} height={plotHeight} fill="transparent" className="cursor-crosshair" onMouseMove={...} onMouseLeave={...} />
  </svg>
</div>
```

## When adding or editing a chart

- [ ] Plot-area mouse tracking (not only dot hover)
- [ ] Vertical dashed crosshair on hover
- [ ] Positioned HTML tooltip (not `<title>` only)
- [ ] `role="img"` + meaningful `aria-label` on the SVG
- [ ] Reuse existing chart constants (`CHART_WIDTH`, `CHART_HEIGHT`, `PADDING`) from sibling charts

## Charts that must comply

- Outstanding shares (`outstanding-shares-chart`)
- Financial trends (`metric-line-chart`)
- Insider transactions (`insider-transactions-chart`) — reference impl
- Any new chart added under `src/routes/` or `src/components/`
